    "tauschii L3 39.",
    "In modern bread wheat (for example, wheat cultivars CDC Landmark, CDC Stanley and Jagger), this L3 segment is around 8.5 Mb in size.",
    "We identified a group of bread wheat landraces originating from Azerbaijan where the corresponding L3 segment was up to 36.35 Mb in size (Fig. 3e).",
    "This L3 introgression showed various lengths in different bread wheat landraces, reflecting extensive recombination.",
    "We further estimated the cumulative proportion of L3 introgression across a comprehensive set of 126 hexaploid wheat landraces, including the WGS data from the 59 landraces generated in this study and publicly available sequencing data (Supplementary Table 16)."
